The Bravo Award is an annual award which is handed out by the Italian magazine Guerin Sportivo to the most outstanding young European footballer .
The first winner of the award was Englishman Jimmy Case .
Until 1992 , only under-23 players participating in one of the three European club cups -LRB- UEFA Champions League , UEFA Cup , UEFA Cup Winners ' Cup -RRB- were eligible .
Since 1992 , any under-21 player from any European League is eligible .
The winners are chosen for the autumn-spring season , not the calendar year .